{"type":"message","id":"a98480f9","parentId":"89dcff26","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:56:18.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've completed the autonomous learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"43ea0b40b73441531089c3504b81e4a525c3ef7a98144cf571b2d0afc4c3ae51"},{"type":"text","text":"**检测到空闲对话，已完成自主学习。**\n\n已完成以下工作：\n\n1. **搜索了3个领域的最新动态**：\n   - 企业数字化转型（2026政策与趋势）\n   - 智能安防与弱电系统（2026技术趋势）\n   - IT运维服务与MSP智能化（2026趋势）\n\n2. **整理了5条关键信息**并保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`，涵盖：\n   - 国家工业互联网平台行动方案、数据局统一数据产权制度等政策\n   - AI多智能体（Multi-Agent）、垂直领域大模型（DSLM）技术趋势\n   - 智能安防：AIoT主动预判、云-边-端协同、数字孪生普及率超60%\n   - AIOps渗透率40%、Agentic AI兴起、MaaS/OaaS服务化趋势\n   - 对道简网络的参考价值：综合一体化交付能力是核心竞争优势"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5105,"output":224,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49310,"cost":{"input":0.0015314999999999999,"output":0.0002688,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00311973}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775105772725}}
